data.description: Move-in ready, immaculately maintained Custom Built Colonial Home 1.01-acre lot, walk to Lake Anna & Pleasant's Landing. Open floor plan, high ceilings & natural light 4 bedrooms & 3.5 bath. 2 car garage. Walk-out basement game/family room, study/bedroom & full bath Sauna conveys! Kitchen opens to family room, 42-inch cabinets with granite tile counter tops ceramic tile back splash, custom island, hardwood floors and SS appliances. Separate dining room whatever suits your lifestyle. Family room with fireplace, currently electric but easily converted to gas or wood burning. Has a large 4-season room with large windows overlooking the back yard. New 4-ton Bosch HVAC! Outside you will find a beautiful open yard to entertain or just relax and is surrounded by mature trees, providing lots of privacy. Owner has designed a great space/camp site for parking an RV or large vehicle that has built in 30-amp electric with gray water drain installed. In addition, there is a custom stone sitting area with firepit. Further back is a lovely garden area with koi pond and indoor/outdoor chicken coop! No HOA. This home and property are really quite spectacular and lovingly cared for.
